Package org.cesecore.util

Class SimpleTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cesecore.util.SimpleTime
  • public class SimpleTime
extends Object
    Helper class for handling user friendly format of time intervals. The format is in the form 'y* mo* *d *h *m *s *ms' where * is a decimal number and d=days, h=hours, m=minutes, s=seconds, ms=milliseconds. Spaces are optional.
    Version:
    $Id: SimpleTime.java 24744 2016-11-15 14:36:16Z anatom $
